              <li>How many ways are there to select <m>9</m>  employees  and rank them for an internal promotion process .</li>
              <li>How many ways are there to select <m>3</m>  employees  and schedule them one at a time for professional development training.</li>
          </ol>
          
      </p>
      
      
     
      
          
          
          
          
      
  </statement>
